reviewText: Little Einsteins: Team Up for Adventure is a Disney DVD compilation of the popular Disney Junior animated/live action series. In this DVD, Leo, Annie, Quincy and June met Rocket for the first time and he and the Einsteins travel across the world learing about art, music and animals. The special features includes sneak peeks of other Disney DVD favourites like Winnie The Pooh Learning Adventures, Pooh's Grand Adventure, and Mickey Mouse Clubhouse. This Little Einsteins DVD is perfect for fans of the classic Disney programme.
summary: How The Einsteins Came To Be!
